Author: throwawayacct338601
Text: I relate soo hard, but trust me when I say that relapsing isn’t worth it. Body positivity is really hard for me, so in recovery I’ve just been trying to be grateful for it performing its functions, holding all my organs, keeping me alive, shit like that - I know it sounds weird but it does help when I’m spiraling about a candid photo or something. If you ever need to talk, I’m here.
